parameters:
"What time is it now...? It's already this late...? I must
have slept quite soundly..."

After being raped by Suzuki at the factory, I was sent home
by his underlings in a car. As soon as I arrived home, I
rushed into the bathroom and washed every inch of my body,
but the deep-seated discomfort wouldn't go away.

Even after waking up from a long sleep the next morning, I
still felt terrible. It was almost noon, but I wanted to
sleep a little more, so I tried to cover myself with the
futon again. However, as if on cue, my smartphone chimed
with a notification.
"Who is it...? It can't be from Suzuki...?"

With trepidation, I picked up my smartphone and saw an
unfamiliar sender's name displayed. When I opened the
message screen, several images had been sent, and as I
tapped to display the images, my face turned pale in an
instant.

Photos of me with semen dripping from my crotch, rolling my
eyes back with a sloppy expression. Not just one or two, but
a vast number of them had been sent to my smartphone. I
immediately called the sender and shouted angrily, though
quietly.

"You! After raping me, you even took these photos! How
rotten can you be! Delete these images right now!"

"Hey, hey, don't start yelling all of a sudden. You'll
damage my ears."

The one who answered my call was, as expected, Suzuki. Just
hearing his voice made the events of yesterday flash back,
but I managed to suppress the rising fear and disgust with
sheer willpower and hurled insults at Suzuki.

"The one who's messed up is your head!! Delete the images
quickly or I'll report you to the police!!"

"Hahaha, that's rich. As if you have the courage to go to
the police in the first place."

"You know what I mean, right? If you go snitching to the
police, your photos will end up spread all over the school
and the internet."

"...Hmph, go ahead and try. I won't be intimidated by
threats like that..."

"Then how about I send those images to your childhood friend
right now? I can't wait to see the look on their face when
they see your ahegao."

"Stop, stop it!! Anything but that!! Don't show it to
Mamoru!!"

"Hahaha, you're pretty desperate. You really don't want him
to see the photos of your rape, huh?"

"If that's the case, submit to me. From today on, you're my
pig slave."
"Ah, maybe I should just spread the photos now..."
"I understand! I'll submit... I'll become your slave...!"

"Hahaha, that's right, that's the way. Anyway, I'm busy with
various things today..."

"Let's see... Come to my house tomorrow. You have a life
too, so we'll work out the details then."

"So, I've said what I wanted to say and I'm going to hang up
now. Remember, if you don't come, I'll spread the photos.
Hahahahaha!"

After ending the call with Suzuki, I fled back into my bed.
The rape alone was painful enough, but now an even worse
hell was beginning. Unable to endure the reality before me,
I sobbed and fell back into sleep.
